sources.title: Know Your Enemy | Full Movie | Crime Drama | Farshad Farahat
sources.description:
Know Your Enemy - A Middle Eastern man invades the home of a young, affluent couple as a result of a road rage incident, and the results are a tense exploration of their preconceptions and misconceptions.
2019.  Stars: Farshad Farahat, Nora-Jane Noone, Maury Sterling
